{"tid":2103274,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"［佛都有火］林作被痴女長文抹黑發火反擊！！！","createTime":"2020-07-11T05:42:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-14T07:46:14.000Z","uid":56716,"like":1,"dislike":50,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"7ffe073863028eb27b2daacb69650691bdffcf97","tid":2103274,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T05:42:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6k1guXN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6k1guXN.jpg&h=fc0e5a9a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hh7b3hN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhh7b3hN.jpg&h=8eab16de&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/73oe04t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F73oe04t.jpg&h=69679ec2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/epnO5v8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FepnO5v8.jpg&h=38acc0cc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m3BPPXO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm3BPPXO.jpg&h=f0ef8b67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AUvdyr9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAUvdyr9.jpg&h=f85ceac4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n正所謂出嚟行最緊要係聲譽，最怕被人惡意抹黑。林作（作仔）一向作風大膽思想獨特，面對各種唔同嘅聲音都一笑置之，但講到抹黑影響其聲譽，作仔絕不退縮。<br />\n有位名為Vanessayam（下稱V女士）嘅女士，早前約咗作仔出嚟傾保險，仲同作仔影合照留念，狀甚融洽。殊不知轉個頭，V女士竟然喺ig發表長文「唱衰」作仔，內容大致係話作仔工作態度唔夠專業，只係一個「有名氣」「有富媽媽照住」嘅二世祖，最令人不解嘅係講講下作仔，忽然轉sell自己教琴12年有幾得人歡心，踩低作仔抬高自己不特止，仲要hashtag 埋林X保險，擺明有心置作仔於死地。<br />\n睇返作仔facebook，V女士早前曾經留言對作仔下線外型「嫌三嫌四」，教人執look，未知V女士想傾保險定搵牛郎呢？當時V女士喺fb留言仲叫人傾保險最好搵返林作本人，又自吹自擂話作仔都要俾面佢，轉頭喺ig卻鬧爆作仔，實在令人摸不著頭腦。作仔佛都有火，即時留言反擊V女士，指其十分無禮貌兼噁心，V女心虛即時刪post兼急發道歉聲明。<br />\n其實作仔咁大反應，因為保險業係佢嘅心血，見過作仔真人都知佢十分專業，貼地無架子，凡事親力親為唔假手於人，做事有效率，會記住客戶講嘅嘢並貼心跟進，凌晨四點仲會覆客戶，咁盡心盡力省靚個招牌，畀人無中生有抹黑，唔嬲就假。"},{"pid":"c3f24423f1ed5c9901417987877f03607b1fd9fd","tid":2103274,"uid":2889,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T05:43:51.000Z","msg":"林作真人出黎回應下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89d14b5225cc8a3090cf6fcee262ffb40b55160c","tid":2103274,"uid":106633,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T05:43:53.000Z","msg":"吉嬸又發姣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2992d388e068ff1c2ea53884b8c8eba8819978f6","tid":2103274,"uid":56716,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"c3f24423f1ed5c9901417987877f03607b1fd9fd","tid":2103274,"uid":2889,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T05:43:51.000Z","msg":"林作真人出黎回應下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T05:44:20.000Z","msg":"支持作仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b9166f71f66619ff4bd9b722fb5607d405e2fa3","tid":2103274,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"89d14b5225cc8a3090cf6fcee262ffb40b55160c","tid":2103274,"uid":106633,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T05:43:53.000Z","msg":"吉嬸又發姣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T05:44:47.000Z","msg":"我係力撐作仔嘅一方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86d775fdde4e4aa189f3402584a7d550c06a21e3","tid":2103274,"uid":23445,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T05:48:38.000Z","msg":"你食屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eff090bf6a2a2c0faf4377720e2a63f22542db52","tid":2103274,"uid":34571,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T05:50:14.000Z","msg":"樓主咪果個痴女"},{"pid":"da1ce5ad6cdc4ee942e9240306d6ce1e776100a0","tid":2103274,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"86d775fdde4e4aa189f3402584a7d550c06a21e3","tid":2103274,"uid":23445,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T05: